{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"503f3d9fc8","title":"对军委准备在沈阳市建立中心血库的批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"c355d73f5f","index":0,"year":1953,"month":3,"day":6,"articleId":"503f3d9fc8"}],"tags":[{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji33","name":"毛泽东全集第33卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/33-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji33":{"comments":[{"id":"81d2a79f97","publicationId":"maoquanji33","articleId":"503f3d9fc8","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"这个批语写在中共中央办公厅第一办公室对东北局批转沈阳市委关于为抗美援朝动员献血计划的摘报上。摘报说：中央军委决定在沈阳市建立一个规模巨大的中心血库。根据抗美援朝前方的需要，拟先由机关、部队、学校开始，动员献血，计划每天300人，采取6万毫升。沈阳市委要求将动员献血与抗美援朝的思想教育结合起来，在动员中必须严格遵守自觉自愿原则，反对单纯任务观点和强迫命令作风。"},{"id":"2e5408c772","publicationId":"maoquanji33","articleId":"503f3d9fc8","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"彭，指彭德怀，当时任人民革命军事委员会副主席。"}],"contents":[{"id":"a40e54e705","type":"title","text":"对军委准备在沈阳市建立中心血库的批语”","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji33","articleId":"503f3d9fc8"},{"id":"81d2a79f97","type":"paragraph","text":"此事请彭注意，督促有关机关予以审查，起草复电。是否需要建立如此巨大的血库，请加翻的。","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji33","articleId":"503f3d9fc8"},{"id":"2e5408c772","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji33","articleId":"503f3d9fc8"},{"id":"58131d5ec2","type":"paragraph","text":"三月六日","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji33","articleId":"503f3d9fc8"}],"page":{"id":"f1a8ba941d","publicationId":"maoquanji33","articleId":"503f3d9fc8","start":47,"end":47}}}},"__N_SSG":true}